title: Dollar Little Changed Ahead of Fed Minutes

organizations.name: dollar little changed ahead of fed

text:
The dollar was little changed Tuesday, as investors stayed on the sidelines ahead of minutes from the Federal Reserve’s most recent meeting.
The WSJ Dollar Index, which gauges the U.S. currency against a basket of 16 others, was unchanged at 87.01.
